    "description": "A unique roguelike game that blends deep strategic deckbuilding with fast-paced auto-battling.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Craft cards to create a huge variety of combos.<br></li><li>Discover and upgrade game-changing items.<br></li><li>Challenge traditional deckbuilding wisdom: thin decks offer speed but lower health and item proficiency.<br></li><li>Freely buy, sell, and combine cards to forge your perfect deck.<br></li><li>Choose from 5 different classes and 2 art styles: classic fantasy or animal champions.</li></ul><br>CardCraft Champions is a fresh strategic challenge.<br>Will you build a lean, efficient deck, wield the most powerful items, or discover a perfect balance?<br><br>Craft cards into unique combinations.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113480/extras/d46a9f654bf80e0119be0bb828339905.avif?t=1763683805\" width=578 height=202 /></span><br><br>Items can upgrade up to tier 6.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113480/extras/b061355ade6dac028c873d5c5522821d.avif?t=1763683805\" width=568 height=426 /></span><br><br>5 classes of characters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113480/extras/f251ff981b6c893f5aa26ff11de738ad.avif?t=1763683805\" width=576 height=112 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113480/extras/2a7df49ea02a2cd0187d6bfc6345853a.avif?t=1763683805\" width=578 height=112 /></span>",
